    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"spell-description\">\n  <p>\n    <strong>School</strong>&nbsp;illusion&nbsp;(glamer);\n    <strong>Level</strong>&nbsp;witch 3;\n    \n    \n    \n    \n  </p>\n  <p>\n    <strong>Casting Time</strong>&nbsp;1 standard action<br>\n    <strong>Components</strong>&nbsp;V, S<br>\n  </p>\n  <p>\n    <strong>Range</strong>&nbsp;close (25 ft. + 5 ft./2 levels)<br>\n    \n    <strong>Targets</strong>&nbsp;one skull<br>\n    \n    <strong>Duration</strong>&nbsp;permanent until discharged<br>\n    <strong>Saving Throw</strong>&nbsp;Will negates;&nbsp;<strong>Spell Resistance</strong>&nbsp;yes<br>\n  </p>\n  <h2>Description</h2>\n  <p>This spell functions as <i>magic mouth</i>, except rather than creating an illusory mouth on any surface, it affects a skull.</p><p>In addition, when the skull's magic is triggered, it releases wild and unnerving cackles before speaking its message.</p><p>All creatures that can hear the cackles must save or become shaken for 1d4 rounds.</p>\n</div>\n",
